---
description: 
alwaysApply: true
---

- Only modify the minimum required code to solve the task
- Do not rewrite entire files unless explicitly asked
- Prefer small diffs over full rewrites
- Follow existing project patterns and structure
- Do not add unnecessary comments or logs
- Ask for clarification if the task is ambiguous
- When fixing bugs, identify root cause before suggesting fix
- When implementing features, break into small steps
- Avoid touching unrelated files
